To set up: 
download Stellar Neopixels folder
save it to the desktop

open terminal

type:
sudo nano /etc/rc.local

paste:
python /home/pi/Desktop/Stellar Neopixels/run_neopixels.py&

control x, y, enter

in terminal

type:
sudo apt-get install rpi.gpio

in main menu:
preferances<raspberry pi configuration<interfaces
enable all

shut down pi
unplug hdmi
wait 1 min before trying buttons